#: templates/dahsolar/dah-factories.html:199
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                        DAH Solar has 4 high-end technology "
"factories with fully automatic workshops and equipment. Annually DAH Solar’s "
"intelligent factories could produce<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New "
"Roman&quot;;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;5.5 GW capacity "
"for TOPCon solar cells, 10 GW TOPCon PV modules(over all is 2024 simiyearly "
"production goal).\n"
"                                    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DAH Solar to'liq avtomatik ustaxonalar va uskunalarga ega 4 ta yuqori "
"texnologiyali zavodga ega. Har yili DAH Solar’ning aqlli zavodlari<span "
"style=\"font-family:&quot; Times New Roman&quot;; font-size:18px; background-"
"color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp; TOPCon quyosh batareyalari uchun 5,5 GVt quvvat, 10 "
"GVt TOPCon sim PV modullarini ishlab chiqarishi mumkin (hammasi yiliga 10 "
"GVt TOPCon sim2 PV modullarini ishlab chiqarish)."

#: templates/dahsolar/dah-factories.html:205
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                        DAH Solar is conjecting the "
"cultivation of the mass production of N-type PV modules, Integrative "
"microinverters, and solar storage in the next few years. DAH Solar aims to "
"provide a low-carbon lifestyle, so we maintain our intelligent factories "
"environment friendly, low-carbon, and green.\n"
"                                    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DAH Solar kelgusi bir necha yil ichida N-tipli PV modullarini, Integrativ "
"mikroinverterlarni va quyosh batareyasini saqlashni ommaviy ishlab "
"chiqarishni o'stirishni taxmin qilmoqda. DAH Solar kam uglerodli turmush "
"tarzini ta'minlashga qaratilgan, shuning uchun biz aqlli zavodlarimizni "
"atrof-muhitga mos, kam uglerodli va yashil rangda saqlaymiz."

#: templates/dahsolar/dah-factories.html:216
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                            DAH factories maintain high "
"productivity by equipping factories with advanced automatic equipment. We "
"grasp the leading manufacturing technique. DAH Solar committees provide high-"
"quality PV products, so we have strict inspections and quality control "
"protocols. Our highly efficient logistics guarantee the fastest delivery to "
"customers all over the world.\n"
"                                            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DAH zavodlari zavodlarni ilg'or avtomatik uskunalar bilan jihozlash orqali "
"yuqori mahsuldorlikni saqlaydi. Biz etakchi ishlab chiqarish texnologiyasini "
"tushunamiz. DAH Quyosh qo'mitalari yuqori sifatli PV mahsulotlarini taqdim "
"etadi, shuning uchun bizda qattiq tekshiruvlar va sifat nazorati "
"protokollari mavjud. Bizning yuqori samarali logistikamiz butun dunyo "
"bo'ylab mijozlarga eng tez yetkazib berishni kafolatlaydi."

