#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:195
msgid "Global Technology Leading PV Enterprise"
msgstr "Global texnologik yetakchi PV korxonasi"

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:202
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                    &nbsp;focuses on the R&amp;D, "
"manufacturing, and sales of high-efficiency power generation PV modules, "
"integrated PV systems, and solar energy storage systems. DAH Solar "
"committees to provide better solar solutions innovatively. With more and "
"more needs for clean energy, DAH Solar continues to bring a more efficient, "
"convenient, and reliable series of PV products to global users.\n"
"                                    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"&nbsp; R&D, ishlab chiqarish va yuqori samarali energiya ishlab chiqarish PV "
"modullarini, integratsiyalashgan PV tizimlari va quyosh energiyasini saqlash "
"tizimlarini sotishga e'tibor qaratadi. DAH Quyosh qo'mitalari innovatsion "
"ravishda yaxshiroq quyosh echimlarini taqdim etish uchun. Toza energiyaga "
"bo'lgan ehtiyoj tobora ortib borayotgani sababli, DAH Solar global "
"foydalanuvchilarga yanada samarali, qulay va ishonchli PV mahsulotlarini "
"taqdim etishda davom etmoqda."

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:211
msgid "Technological innovation and patented products"
msgstr "Texnologik innovatsiyalar va patentlangan mahsulotlar"

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:216
#, python-format
msgid "With our leading technological innovation and excellent product quality, we enable global users more conveniently and stably to obtain efficient clean solar energy. We have 200 patented technologies used in our PV products. Our global patented product Full-Screen PV module achieves front A-side frameless design, which increases power generation by 6%%-15%% (field test result published by TUV Nord) compared to the regular PV modules. The world's first integrated PV system, SolarUnit, could maximize the installation area of the rooftop. SolarUnit made the integrated design of modules and inverters come true. SolarUnit provides users with a more efficient, convenient, safer, and beautiful residential PV system. SolarUnit promotes PV products in the era of home PV appliances."
msgstr 
"Yetakchi texnologik innovatsiyalarimiz va ajoyib mahsulot sifatimiz bilan "
"biz global foydalanuvchilarga samarali toza quyosh energiyasini yanada qulay "
"va barqaror olish imkonini beramiz. Bizning PV mahsulotlarimizda "
"ishlatiladigan 200 ta patentlangan texnologiyamiz mavjud. Bizning global "
"patentlangan mahsulotimiz To'liq ekranli PV moduli old tomonda A-tomoni "
"ramkasiz dizaynni amalga oshiradi, bu esa odatiy PV modullariga nisbatan "
"energiya ishlab chiqarishni 6%%-15%% ga oshiradi (TUV Nord tomonidan e'lon "
"qilingan maydon sinov natijasi). Dunyodagi birinchi integratsiyalashgan PV "
"tizimi, SolarUnit, tomning o'rnatish maydonini maksimal darajada oshirishi "
"mumkin. SolarUnit modullar va invertorlarning integratsiyalashgan dizaynini "
"amalga oshirdi. SolarUnit foydalanuvchilarga yanada samarali, qulay, xavfsiz "
"va chiroyli turar-joy PV tizimini taqdim etadi. SolarUnit uy PV qurilmalari "
"davrida PV mahsulotlarini targ'ib qiladi."

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:225
msgid "World Recognized PV Supplier"
msgstr "Dunyoda tan olingan PV yetkazib beruvchi"

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:229
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                DAH Solar's products have been sold in more "
"than 100 countries and regions around the world. In Latin America, we have "
"become the TOP 3 well-known PV companies in Brazil. In Europe, the demand "
"for our innovative products, Full-Screen PV Modules, is exceeding supplies. "
"Besides, to provide better service to global customers, we have established "
"our warehouses in many countries and regions, like the EU stock in Rotterdam "
"in the Netherlands. In addition, we have established very convenient "
"purchase channels for global consumers. Customers can purchase DAH Solar’s "
"products through distributors or official websites and E-commercial "
"platforms.\n"
"                                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DAH Solar mahsulotlari dunyoning 100 dan ortiq mamlakatlari va mintaqalarida "
"sotilgan. Lotin Amerikasida biz Braziliyadagi TOP 3 ta taniqli PV "
"kompaniyalariga aylandik. Evropada bizning innovatsion mahsulotlarimizga, "
"To'liq ekranli PV modullariga bo'lgan talab takliflardan oshib ketadi. "
"Bundan tashqari, global mijozlarga yaxshiroq xizmat ko'rsatish uchun biz "
"Gollandiyaning Rotterdam shahridagi EI aktsiyalari kabi ko'plab mamlakatlar "
"va mintaqalarda o'z omborlarimizni tashkil etdik. Bundan tashqari, biz "
"global iste'molchilar uchun juda qulay xarid kanallarini yaratdik. Mijozlar "
"DAH Solar mahsulotlarini distribyutorlar yoki rasmiy veb-saytlar va elektron "
"tijorat platformalari orqali sotib olishlari mumkin."

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:237
msgid "Social Responsibilities"
msgstr "Ijtimoiy mas'uliyat"

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:241
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                DAH Solar’s Solar Cells, Modules, and "
"Inverters R&amp;D and Production Factories Bases not only attract a large "
"number of local high-end technical talents but also creates more than 2,000 "
"job positions for local residents. Every year, we hold many social "
"activities, such as donations to charities, responses to the Covid-19 "
"pandemic, contributing to community growth, etc. to advocate for social "
"development. Our ultimate goal is to embrace the era of clean energy to "
"protect the environment and the behalf of mankind.\n"
"                                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DAH Quyoshning quyosh batareyalari, modullari va invertorlari ilmiy-tadqiqot "
"va ishlab chiqarish zavodlari bazalari nafaqat ko'plab mahalliy yuqori "
"darajadagi texnik iste'dodlarni jalb qiladi, balki mahalliy aholi uchun 2000 "
"dan ortiq ish o'rinlarini yaratadi. Biz har yili ijtimoiy rivojlanishni "
"targ'ib qilish uchun xayriya tashkilotlariga xayr-ehsonlar, Covid-19 "
"pandemiyasiga qarshi kurash, jamiyatning o'sishiga hissa qo'shish va "
"boshqalar kabi ko'plab ijtimoiy tadbirlarni o'tkazamiz. Bizning yakuniy "
"maqsadimiz atrof-muhit va insoniyat manfaatlarini himoya qilish uchun toza "
"energiya davrini qabul qilishdir."

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:248
msgid "Employee Development"
msgstr "Xodimlarni rivojlantirish"

#: templates/dahsolar/dahsolar.html:253
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                DAH Solar is committed to creating a better "
"career development platform for our employees. We seek equity for all "
"genders and ages in the workplace. DAH Solar offers our employees a free "
"team-building trip, annually. We believe that refreshing is another path to "
"creation. DAH Solar is also concerned about the health condition of our "
"employees. That's why we provide our employees with free health checks and a "
"full package of healthcare. At DAH Solar, we treat our employees not only as "
"team assets but as our own families.\n"
"                                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DAH Solar xodimlarimiz uchun yaxshiroq martaba rivojlantirish platformasini "
"yaratishga intiladi. Biz ish joyida barcha jinslar va yoshdagilar uchun "
"tenglikni qidiramiz. DAH Solar o'z xodimlariga har yili bepul jamoa qurish "
"sayohatini taklif qiladi. Biz yangilanishni yaratishning yana bir yo'li deb "
"hisoblaymiz. DAH Solar ham xodimlarimizning sog'lig'i haqida qayg'uradi. "
"Shuning uchun biz xodimlarimizni bepul tibbiy ko'rikdan o'tkazamiz va tibbiy "
"yordamning to'liq paketini taqdim etamiz. DAH Solar kompaniyasida biz "
"xodimlarimizga nafaqat jamoaning aktivi, balki o'z oilamiz kabi munosabatda "
"bo'lamiz."

#: templates/dahsolar/overview.html:198
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                        Being established in 2009, DAH Solar "
"is an innovation-driven and technology-leading company in PV product "
"manufacturing. The production capacity in 2024 will reach 6GW solar cells, "
"10GW PV modules, 300,000 sets SolarUnit, 5GW silicon wafers and 10GW "
"vertical integration manufacturing base under construction, Solar Unit. DAH "
"Solar contributes to providing high-efficiency PV modules, high-"
"qualitysolarcells, high-techintegrated solars ystems, and high-value energy "
"storage for our value dcustomers. DAH Solar’s products have been sold to "
"more than 120 countries and regions around the world including Germany, "
"Netherlands, Spain, Brazil, Mexico, Australia, Japan and soon.<br>\n"
"                                    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"2009 yilda tashkil etilgan DAH Solar PV mahsulotlarini ishlab chiqarishda "
"innovatsiyalarga asoslangan va texnologiya bo'yicha yetakchi kompaniya "
"hisoblanadi.2024 yilda ishlab chiqarish quvvati 6 GVt quyosh batareyalari, "
"10 GVt PV modullari, 300 000 to'plam SolarUnit, 5 GVt kremniy gofretlari va "
"10 GVt vertikal integratsiyalashgan ishlab chiqarish bazasi qurilayotgan "
"quyosh blokiga etadi. DAH Solar qimmatli mijozlarimiz uchun yuqori samarali "
"PV modullari, yuqori sifatli quyosh batareyalari, yuqori texnologiyali "
"integratsiyalashgan quyosh tizimlari va yuqori qiymatli energiyani saqlashga "
"hissa qo'shadi. DAH Solar mahsulotlari Germaniya, Niderlandiya, Ispaniya, "
"Braziliya, Meksika, Avstraliya, Yaponiya va yaqin orada dunyoning 120 dan "
"ortiq mamlakatlari va mintaqalariga sotilgan.<br>"

#: templates/dahsolar/overview.html:212
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                    Technology innovation has been the most "
"important driving force of the development of DAH Solar. DAH Solar invests "
"more than 15%% annually in&nbsp; research and development. DAH Solar is the "
"founder and the master of the Full-Screen PV Module.The Full-Screen PV "
"Module which has no frame on all sides on the front holds a global patent "
"over 18 countries and regions, it can increase the power generation by "
"6-15%%.<br>\n"
"                                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Texnologiya innovatsiyasi DAH Solar rivojlanishining eng muhim "
"harakatlantiruvchi kuchi bo'ldi. DAH Solar yiliga 15%% dan ortiq sarmoya "
"kiritadi&nbsp; tadqiqot va ishlanmalar. DAH Solar toʻliq ekranli PV "
"modulining asoschisi va ustasi hisoblanadi. Toʻliq ekranli PV moduli old "
"tomonida har tomondan ramkaga ega boʻlmagan 18 mamlakat va mintaqada global "
"patentga ega boʻlib, u energiya ishlab chiqarishni 6-15%% ga oshirishi "
"mumkin.<br>"

#: templates/dahsolar/overview.html:225
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                    Besides, DAH Solar invents the world’s "
"first integrated PV system, SolarUnit. DAH Solar’s products have "
"international authoritative certifications such as TUV, IEC, CE,and INMETRO, "
"domestic industry certifications such as CQC, Leader, ISO9001, ISO14001, "
"ISO45001, etc.<br>\n"
"                                    <br>\n"
"                                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Bundan tashqari, DAH Solar dunyodagi birinchi integratsiyalashgan PV "
"tizimini, SolarUnitni ixtiro qiladi. DAH Solar mahsulotlari TUV, IEC, "
"Idoralar va INMETRO kabi xalqaro nufuzli sertifikatlarga, CQC, Leader, "
"ISO9001, ISO14001, ISO45001 va boshqalar kabi mahalliy sanoat "
"sertifikatlariga ega.<br> <br>"

#: templates/dahsolar/overview.html:236
msgid ""
"\n"
"                                    DAH Solar will always regard the user "
"demand as the key focus of product research and innovation and keep on "
"bringing more efficient, stable and intelligent photovoltaic products.<br>\n"
"                                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"DAH Solar har doim foydalanuvchi talabini mahsulot tadqiqoti va "
"innovatsiyalarining asosiy yo'nalishi sifatida ko'rib chiqadi va yanada "
"samarali, barqaror va aqlli fotovoltaik mahsulotlarni olib kelishda davom "
"etadi.<br>"

